bubbleViewController:
*) holds a bubbleView
*) add touch gesture listener to the view
	*) upon click, call bllbelView#maybePopBubble

bubbleView:
*) create 5 random colored, similar sized bubble upon start
	*) bubble should not overlap with eath other
	*) bubble should be floating around

*) maybePopBubble
	*) findBubble if not nil, remove it
	*) remove the bubble if there is bubble

*) findBubble(CGPoint) -done
	*) returns the bubble that covers the CGPoint or nil

*) tap to add -done

*) long press to clear -done

*) remove(Bubble)
	*) remove from view
	*) add animations

*) addBubble -done
	*) randomly generate a bubble(center, diameter), check if it's overlap with exsiting bubbles
		*) if it overlaps generate another
		*) otherwise create the bubble and display it
	*) give up when hits limit

*) Bubble
	*) diameter, center -done
	*) gravity
		let them drop on button first
	*) maybe floating around
	*) color, shade
	*) moving, collision with other bubbles